### ðŸ†š ReactJS vs React Native

| Feature         | ReactJS                      | React Native                |
|----------------|------------------------------|-----------------------------|
| Purpose         | Web Development              | Mobile App Development      |
| Platform        | Browser (HTML/CSS)           | Android & iOS (Native APIs) |
| Styling         | CSS                          | StyleSheet API              |

