### ðŸ†š ReactJS vs Angular

| Feature        | ReactJS                        | Angular                     |
|----------------|--------------------------------|-----------------------------|
| Type           | Library                        | Framework                   |
| Language       | JavaScript / JSX               | TypeScript                  |
| DOM            | Virtual DOM                    | Real DOM                    |
| Learning Curve | Moderate                       | Steep                       |
